26#include "config.h"
27#include "CachedApplicationManifest.h"
28
29#if ENABLE(APPLICATION_MANIFEST)
30
31#include "ApplicationManifestParser.h"
32#include "SharedBuffer.h"
33#include "TextResourceDecoder.h"
34
35namespace WebCore {
36
37CachedApplicationManifest::CachedApplicationManifest(CachedResourceRequest&& request, PAL::SessionID sessionID, const CookieJar* cookieJar)
38 : CachedResource(WTFMove(request), Type::ApplicationManifest, sessionID, cookieJar)
39 , m_decoder(TextResourceDecoder::create("application/manifest+json", UTF8Encoding()))
40{
41}
42
43void CachedApplicationManifest::finishLoading(SharedBuffer* data, const NetworkLoadMetrics& metrics)
44{
45 m_data = data;
46 setEncodedSize(data ? data->size() : 0);
47 if (data)
48 m_text = m_decoder->decodeAndFlush(data->data(), data->size());
49 CachedResource::finishLoading(data, metrics);
50}
51
52void CachedApplicationManifest::setEncoding(const String& chs)
53{
54 m_decoder->setEncoding(chs, TextResourceDecoder::EncodingFromHTTPHeader);
55}
56
57String CachedApplicationManifest::encoding() const
58{
59 return m_decoder->encoding().name();
60}
61
62std::optional<ApplicationManifest> CachedApplicationManifest::process(const URL& manifestURL, const URL& documentURL, Document* document)
63{
64 if (!m_text)
65 return std::nullopt;
66 if (document)
67 return ApplicationManifestParser::parse(*document, *m_text, manifestURL, documentURL);
68 return ApplicationManifestParser::parse(*m_text, manifestURL, documentURL);
69}
70
71} // namespace WebCore
72
73#endif // ENABLE(APPLICATION_MANIFEST)
